Class VNCQueue

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--gnu.vnc.VNCQueue
public class VNCQueue
extends Object

Smart rectangle queue that converts inserted rectangles to as small a number of encoded RFB rectangles as possible within a specified clipping area.
